  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goal of the project is capacity building of religious education in several Tanzanian communities. The religious education will foster growth in local communities as it is targeted the establishment of small businesses, micro-loan opportunities, small child care institutions and knowledge of how to manage conflicts through dialogue.

Capacity building for establishing small businesses and micro-loan companies.

Education in book keeping, childcare needs and rights, and rights of marginalized groups

Capacity building of religious institutions.

Dialogue training for conflict management.</narrative>
